  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bb5 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd -\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Do not allow the spread of Covid-19 again - President Ranil's request to the people of the country",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Even with the resurgence of covid infection in the country, the interest shown by the people in getting the phase 4 vaccine is very low. President Ranil Wickremesinghe has asked the people of the country to get the vaccines as soon as possible without allowing the covid infection to spread.",
        "In this regard, in a special announcement issued by him today, it is further stated that:",
        "Even with the resurgence of covid infections in the country, the interest shown by people in getting the phase 4 vaccine is very low. While 17 million people have received the primary vaccine, only 22,623 have received the Phase 4 vaccine.",
        "The country currently has 8 million vaccines in stock. They can be used till next October. If these vaccines cannot be fully utilized within that period, they will have to be supplied to other countries. So we request the general public to get vaccinated as soon as possible.",
        "I request everyone to follow the advice given by the Ministry of Health in this regard. Currently there is talk about 'Monkey Measles'. Measures have been taken to prevent the spread of the disease in the country. In addition, arrangements have been made for the treatment of the disease if it is unexpectedly diagnosed.",
        "In any case, he said, he would request the people not to allow the spread of covid infection again in the country and to follow the health regulations properly."
      ],
